                        <interp inst="t18700110-153-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>GUILTY <hi rend="italic">of larceny</hi>
                     </rs> . Recommended to mercy by the Jury on amount of his youth—<rs id="t18700110-153-punishment-22" type="punishmentDescription">
